    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks so much for stopping by to check out my car. Honestly, this has been such a dependable ride for me, and I\u2019ve taken really good care of it! It\u2019s in solid shape and still drives like a dream\u2014perfect for someone who wants a reliable vehicle without the brand-new price tag. It has a few minor signs of love from the road, but it's been well-maintained and is totally ready for its next adventure. I\u2019d love for it to go to a good home, so feel free to reach out if you want to come by and take it for a spin!",
