    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is powered by the high-revving S54 inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and Double VANOS for exceptional throttle response and a linear power delivery to its 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain consists of a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission paired with a variable M-differential lock. Recent mechanical attention includes a reinforced rear subframe and refreshed suspension bushings to maintain the integrity of the chassis' multi-link rear geometry. The braking system remains firm, and the steering rack provides the communicative, unassisted feel expected of this analog icon. A driver-focused example that balances mechanical purity with dependable performance.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 11
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
