    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready for your next adventure? I\u2019m parting with my car and it is honestly in such great shape! It\u2019s been super well-maintained, runs like a dream, and has plenty of life left in it. It\u2019s been my trusty companion for commutes and weekend trips, and I\u2019ve always made sure it was looked after. I\u2019d love for it to go to a new home where it\u2019ll be just as appreciated. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions\u2014I'm happy to chat and show you around the vehicle!",
      "price": 32500.0,
